Isaac Oguntoye Apostle Suleman and wife, Lizzy few days ago celebrated their 15th years wedding anniversary. The Apostle in his anniversary message however pointed he is yet to see a sweet home as his. ‘’My 15years marriage anniversary June 5th 2004….just like yesterday.. yet to see a home as sweet as mine..’’, he wrote while sharing a throwback photo of himself and wife. However, Apostle Suleman is a servant of God and senior pastor at Omega Fire Ministries (OFM) worldwide where he delivers messages of hope and total restoration to all and sundry.